    "Rewrite the Career Summary into a punchy 2‑sentence value proposition that highlights a unique achievement (e.g., the $1.4 M fraud‑detection savings) and the specific role you’re targeting.",
    "Replace the outdated \"References available upon request\" line with a concise statement directing readers to your LinkedIn or portfolio, and ensure the LinkedIn URL includes the full https:// prefix.",
    "Add a brief soft‑skill/leadership bullet (e.g., stakeholder management, mentorship) under each role and consider including a link or short description of a portfolio/GitHub project to showcase your code and models."
  ],
  "rating": 8
